msgid ""
"When working with dense geometry, it can become difficult to make subtle "
"adjustments to the vertices without causing visible lumps and creases in "
"the model's surface. When you face situations like this the Proportional "
"Editing tool can be used to smoothly deform the surface of the model. "
"This is done by the tool's automatic modification of unselected vertices "
"within a given range."
